// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// MOCK DATASET
// In production this comes from an indexed store (Postgres full-text index /
// Elasticsearch / Meilisearch). Ranking here mirrors what the backend scorer
// would do — see RANKING NOTES at the bottom of this file.
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
